# -*- RD -*-

= README

== Loudmouth-Ruby -- Ruby bindings for Loudmouth
These are the Ruby bindings for Loudmouth, an asynchronous XMPP library written in C.

== Install
  
  % ruby extconf.rb
  % make
  % sudo make install
  
=== extconf.rb options

  : --ruby
     ruby directory

  : --topsrcdir
     top source directory

  : --topdir
      top directory

  : --strict
      if some libraries fail to compile/install, "make"
      command returns 1(exit 1)

=== Dependencies

  : Ruby/GLib (part of Ruby-gtk2 or Ruby-gnome2, http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.jp)
  
  : Loudmouth 1.4.0 (The C library, http://www.loudmouth-project.org)

== Bugs

Please report bugs to our bug tracker
http://loudmouth.lighthouseapp.com

